These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: tea, cola, milk, mirinda
Pet: chinchilla, hamster, ferret, rat
1. Pet:rat is on the left of Beverage:milk##1
2. Beverage:tea is on the left of Pet:hamster##1
3. Beverage:mirinda is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:ferret is on the left or right of Pet:rat##3
5. Beverage:tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | tea | cola | mirinda | milk |
| Pet        | chinchilla | hamster   | rat | ferret    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: animation, drama, mystery, adventure
Nationality: italian, thai, colombian, egyptian
1. Movie-Genre:drama is on the left of Movie-Genre:adventure##1
2. Nationality:italian is on the left of Nationality:colombian##1
3. Nationality:colombian is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:italian == Movie-Genre:animation##1
5. Nationality:thai is on the right of Nationality:colombian##1
6. Nationality:italian == Movie-Genre:animation##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | animation  | drama  | adventure |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | italian | colombian | thai    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: pear, cauliflower, cucumber, radish
Movie-Genre: mystery, scientific, musical, fantasy
1. Food:radish is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:fantasy##3
2. Food:cucumber is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:fantasy is on the left or right of Food:cauliflower##3
4. Movie-Genre:fantasy is on the right of Movie-Genre:musical##1
5. Movie-Genre:mystery is in an odd position##4
6. Food:cauliflower is on the right of Food:cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | radish | cucumber | cauliflower    | pear      |
| Movie-Genre   | musical        | fantasy     | mystery | scientific |

