.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: fishing, magic-tricks, video-games, puzzles
Music-Genre: jazz, d&b, techno, metal
1. Hobby:magic-tricks is between Music-Genre:jazz and Music-Genre:metal##2
2. Hobby:puzzles is on the left of Hobby:fishing##1
3. Music-Genre:techno is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:d&b is on the left of Music-Genre:metal##1
5. Music-Genre:d&b is on the right of Hobby:fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | puzzles | fishing | magic-tricks | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | techno       | jazz   | d&b    | metal  |

