.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Music-Genre: salsa, gospel, r&b, classical
Nationality: malaysian, italian, dutch, canadian
1. Music-Genre:r&b is on the right of Nationality:canadian##1
2. Nationality:italian == Music-Genre:classical##1
3. Nationality:dutch is on the right of Music-Genre:salsa##1
4. Music-Genre:gospel is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:r&b is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:malaysian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | salsa    | r&b   | classical       |
| Nationality   | malaysian | canadian | dutch | italian |

