.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Beverage: lemonade, tea, water, iced-tea
Music-Genre: folk, metal, rock, r&b
1. Beverage:lemonade == Music-Genre:r&b##1
2. Music-Genre:folk is on the right of Beverage:lemonade##1
3. Music-Genre:r&b is between Music-Genre:folk and Beverage:water##2
4. Beverage:lemonade is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:r&b is on the left or right of Music-Genre:folk##3
6. Beverage:tea is on the left or right of Music-Genre:metal##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | tea       | water   | lemonade | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre   | rock | metal | r&b        | folk    |

