.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Beverage: sprite, coffee, soy-milk, juice
Food: pineapple, avocado, peach, plum
1. Food:avocado is on the far left##1
2. Beverage:soy-milk is on the left or right of Beverage:sprite##3
3. Beverage:juice is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:peach is on the left of Food:plum##1
5. Food:plum is on the right of Beverage:sprite##1
6. Food:peach is in an even position##4
7. Food:pineapple == Beverage:coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | juice | sprite    | soy-milk       | coffee |
| Food       | avocado  | peach | plum | pineapple  |

